description: The index’s initial investable universe consists of equity securities and depositary receipts of companies listed on exchanges in Australia, Brazil, Canada, Hong Kong, Israel, Japan, Mexico, New Zealand, Republic of South Korea, Singapore, Switzerland, United Kingdom, United States of America, or any member country of the European Union. At least 80% of the fund’s net assets, plus borrowings for investment purposes, will be invested in Airline Companies, Hotel Companies or Cruise Line Companies. It is non-diversified.
name: SonicShares Airlines, Hotels, Cruise Lines ETF
